Package ba.unsa.etf.rpr.domain

Class Tickets

java.lang.Object
ba.unsa.etf.rpr.domain.Tickets
All Implemented Interfaces:
Idable
public class Tickets extends Object implements Idable
The Tickets class represents a ticket for a flight. It implements the Idable interface, which requires the implementation of the `getId` and `setId` methods.
